<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Haguenau Sharks | Official AHL Website</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhana:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --shark-black: #0A0A0A;
            --shark-red: #D32F2F;
            --shark-white: #FFFFFF;
            --shark-silver: #C0C0C0;
            --shark-gray: #1A1A1A;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: var(--shark-black);
            color: var(--shark-white);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Background Pattern */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="M50 10 L70 40 L80 50 L50 80 L35 60 L20 50 Z" fill="rgba(211,47,47,0.03)"/></svg>') repeat,
                repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 100px, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.02) 100px, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.02) 102px),
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
            background-size: 200px 200px, 100%, 100%, 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            animation: bgMove 30s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bgMove {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }

        .loading {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--shark-black);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 9999;
            opacity: 1;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
        }

        .loading.hidden {
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .loading-logo {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: spin 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.8));
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1.15); }
        }

        .loading-text {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: var(--shark-red);
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.8);
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--shark-red);
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 15px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .header.scrolled {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.98);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .header .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .logo-img {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.6));
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 32px;
            color: var(--shark-red);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
        }

        .nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .nav-link {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            color: var(--shark-white);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 5px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-link::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 5px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--shark-red);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-link:hover::after {
            width: 60%;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--shark-red);
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 150px 20px 80px;
            background: 
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.25) 0%, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9) 100%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 800px;
            height: 800px;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 200 200"><path d="M100 30 L140 90 L160 100 L100 140 L70 110 L50 100 Z" fill="rgba(211,47,47,0.1)"/></svg>') center/contain no-repeat;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            animation: rotate 40s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid var(--shark-red);
            border-radius: 50px;
            color: var(--shark-red);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.7); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 20px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0); }
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: clamp(50px, 10vw, 120px);
            color: var(--shark-red);
            text-shadow: 
                0 0 40px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.9),
                0 0 80px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 48px);
            color: var(--shark-white);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 50px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-stat {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            min-width: 120px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .hero-stat:hover {
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
            border-color: var(--shark-red);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .hero-stat-value {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 48px;
            color: var(--shark-red);
            display: block;
        }

        .hero-stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--shark-silver);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D32F2F, #B71C1C);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.5);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.8);
        }

        /* Section Styles */
        .section {
            padding: 100px 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 56px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--shark-red);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--shark-silver);
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .section-divider {
            width: 120px;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D32F2F, #B71C1C);
            margin: 20px auto 60px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* Roster Section */
        .roster {
            background: var(--shark-gray);
        }

        .roster-filters {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .filter-btn {
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--shark-red);
            color: var(--shark-white);
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .filter-btn:hover,
        .filter-btn.active {
            background: var(--shark-red);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .roster-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .player-card {
            background: var(--shark-black);
            border: 2px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .player-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--shark-red);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.4);
        }

        .player-image {
            height: 300px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2), var(--shark-black));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 100px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .player-number {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 56px;
            color: var(--shark-red);
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.7);
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .player-info {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .player-name {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--shark-white);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .player-position {
            color: var(--shark-red);
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .player-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
        }

        .player-stat {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .player-stat-value {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--shark-red);
            display: block;
        }

        .player-stat-value.positive {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .player-stat-value.negative {
            color: #f44336;
        }

        .player-stat-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #999;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Standings */
        .standings {
            background: var(--shark-black);
        }

        .standings-tabs {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            color: var(--shark-white);
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .tab-btn:hover,
        .tab-btn.active {
            background: var(--shark-red);
            border-color: var(--shark-red);
        }

        .standings-table {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 2px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .standings-header {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 60px 2fr 80px 80px 80px 80px 100px;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--shark-red);
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .standings-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 60px 2fr 80px 80px 80px 80px 100px;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .standings-row:hover {
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08);
        }

        .standings-row.highlighted {
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.15);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--shark-red);
        }

        .standings-position {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: var(--shark-red);
        }

        .standings-team {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--shark-white);
        }

        .standings-stat {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--shark-silver);
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        /* News Section */
        .news {
            background: var(--shark-gray);
        }

        .news-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .news-card {
            background: var(--shark-black);
            border: 2px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .news-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--shark-red);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.4);
        }

        .news-image {
            height: 250px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2), var(--shark-black));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 80px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .news-category {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            background: var(--shark-red);
            color: white;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .news-content {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .news-date {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .news-title {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: var(--shark-white);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .news-excerpt {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .news-link {
            color: var(--shark-red);
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .news-link:hover {
            color: var(--shark-white);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: var(--shark-black);
            border-top: 3px solid var(--shark-red);
            padding: 50px 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer p {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        /* Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 50px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
            }
            
            .roster-grid,
            .news-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .standings-header {
                display: none;
            }

            .standings-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 10px;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .standings-stat::before {
                content: attr(data-label) ': ';
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--shark-red);
            }

            .player-stats {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
        }
    
/* ============================
   NHL PRO PACK (safe patch)
============================ */
.hero {
    background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, rgba(211,47,47,.22), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%, rgba(0,188,212,.12), transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,.55), rgba(0,0,0,.92)),
        url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,') center/cover no-repeat !important;
}
.hero::before {
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    inset:0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.03), rgba(255,255,255,.03) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 4px);
    opacity:.12;
    pointer-events:none;
}
.player-card{cursor:pointer}
.player-card:hover{transform:translateY(-10px); box-shadow:0 30px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.75)}

/* Modal override: fields only */
.modal-backdrop{
  position:fixed; inset:0;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.72);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  z-index:2000; opacity:0; pointer-events:none;
  transition: opacity .2s ease;
}
.modal-backdrop.open{opacity:1; pointer-events:auto}
.modal{
  position:fixed; left:50%; top:50%;
  transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(.98);
  width:min(720px, 92vw);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20,20,20,.95), rgba(8,8,8,.96));
  border:2px solid rgba(211,47,47,.35);
  border-radius:18px;
  z-index:2100; opacity:0; pointer-events:none;
  transition: opacity .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 30px 120px rgba(0,0,0,.75);
}
.modal.open{opacity:1; pointer-events:auto; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1)}
.modal .modal-header{
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
  padding:18px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  background: rgba(211,47,47,.10);
}
.modal .modal-title h3{
  font-family:'Bebas Neue', cursive;
  font-size:34px; letter-spacing:2px;
}
.modal .modal-title p{color:#c0c0c0; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-top:4px}
.modal .modal-close{
  width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
  color:#fff; cursor:pointer;
}
.modal .modal-body{padding:18px}
.modal .panel{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  border-radius:14px;
  padding:16px;
}
.modal .panel h4{
  font-family:'Bebas Neue', cursive;
  letter-spacing:2px;
  font-size:20px;
  color: var(--shark-red);
  margin-bottom:10px;
}
.modal .kv{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px}
.modal .k{color:#aaa; font-size:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px}
.modal .v{font-family:'Bebas Neue', cursive; font-size:22px; letter-spacing:1px}



/* Animated gradient energy */
body {
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(211,47,47,0.18), transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 80% 60%, rgba(0,188,212,0.15), transparent 50%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #050505 0%, #0a0a0a 60%, #040404 100%);
  background-attachment: fixed;
}

/* subtle moving light sweep */
body::before {
  content: "";
  position: fixed;
  inset: -20%;
  pointer-events: none;
  background: linear-gradient(
      120deg,
      transparent 0%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 30%,
      transparent 60%
  );
  animation: iceSweep 14s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes iceSweep {
  0% { transform: translateX(-40%); }
  100% { transform: translateX(40%); }
}

/* arena spotlight glow */
.section::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% -20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), transparent 60%);
}

/* subtle particle dots (ice texture feeling) */
body::after {
  content: "";
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 3px 3px;
  opacity: 0.15;
}

/* hockey neon accent pulse */
.header {
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(211,47,47,0.15);
  animation: headerGlow 6s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes headerGlow {
  0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(211,47,47,0.10); }
  50% { box-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(211,47,47,0.25); }
}

   MODE ARENA PRO (VISIBLE)
   - only d√©cor / ambiance
============================== */

/* stronger base */
body{
  background:
    radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 18% 22%, rgba(211,47,47,0.32), transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(1100px 650px at 82% 55%, rgba(0,188,212,0.24), transparent 58%),
    radial-gradient(900px 520px at 55% 85%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #040404 0%, #090909 55%, #030303 100%) !important;
  background-attachment: fixed;
}

/* animated gradient blobs (very visible) */
body::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:-30%;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 25%, rgba(211,47,47,0.35), transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 75% 55%, rgba(0,188,212,0.26), transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 55% 80%, rgba(211,47,47,0.18), transparent 55%);
  filter: blur(12px);
  opacity: .95;
  animation: arenaFloat 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  z-index:-1;
}

@keyframes arenaFloat{
  0%{transform: translate3d(-2%, -1%, 0) scale(1.00)}
  100%{transform: translate3d(2%, 1.5%, 0) scale(1.06)}
}

/* moving light sweep (stronger) */
body::after{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:-20%;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    linear-gradient(115deg,
      transparent 0%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 28%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 38%,
      transparent 60%);
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
  animation: iceSweepPro 6.5s linear infinite;
  z-index:-1;
}

@keyframes iceSweepPro{
  0%{transform: translateX(-30%) rotate(2deg)}
  100%{transform: translateX(30%) rotate(2deg)}
}

/* arena spotlights per section (visible but subtle) */
.section{
  position:relative;
}
.section::after{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  inset:-1px;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(900px 420px at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.10), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(900px 520px at 0% 40%, rgba(211,47,47,0.10), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(900px 520px at 100% 55%, rgba(0,188,212,0.08), transparent 62%);
  opacity:.9;
}

/* ice grain texture (more visible) */
html::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  pointer-events:none;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 4px 4px;
  opacity: .22;
  z-index:-1;
}

/* header glow stronger */
.header{
  box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(211,47,47,0.20) !important;
}
.header.scrolled{
  box-shadow: 0 0 70px rgba(211,47,47,0.26) !important;
}

/* subtle hover sparkle without touching layout */
.player-card:hover{
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.10), 0 18px 60px rgba(211,47,47,0.18) !important;
}



/* ==============================
   ARENA PRO FORCE (VISIBLE FIX)
   Forces background even if containers are black
============================== */

/* apply animated arena background to BODY AND MAIN WRAPPERS */
html, body,
main,
.site,
.wrapper,
.container,
.app,
#app,
.page-wrapper {
  background:
    radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 18% 22%, rgba(211,47,47,0.35), transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(1100px 650px at 82% 55%, rgba(0,188,212,0.30), transparent 58%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #040404 0%, #090909 55%, #020202 100%) !important;
}

/* animated arena lights */
html::before {
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:-25%;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 25%, rgba(211,47,47,0.35), transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 75% 55%, rgba(0,188,212,0.30), transparent 50%);
  filter: blur(14px);
  animation: arenaMove 9s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  z-index:-1;
}

@keyframes arenaMove{
  0%{transform: translate(-3%, -2%) scale(1)}
  100%{transform: translate(3%, 2%) scale(1.05)}
}

/* moving light sweep */
body::after {
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:-20%;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.10) 30%, transparent 60%);
  animation: arenaSweep 7s linear infinite;
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
  z-index:-1;
}

@keyframes arenaSweep{
  0%{transform: translateX(-40%)}
  100%{transform: translateX(40%)}
}



/* ==============================
   ARENA GLASS FIX (makes color visible)
   - only changes container backgrounds
============================== */

/* Target common wrappers/sections that often have solid black backgrounds */
.section,
.section *,
.roster,
.roster-section,
.roster-wrapper,
.main,
.main-content,
.content,
.content-wrapper,
.page,
.page-section,
.container,
.wrapper,
.site,
#app,
#root{
  /* do NOT blanket override all children backgrounds; only if explicitly set.
     We'll override common solid backgrounds below. */
}

/* Make the big blocks "glass" instead of pure black */
.section,
.roster,
.roster-section,
.roster-wrapper,
.main-content,
.content-wrapper,
.page-section,
.container{
  background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.58) !important;
  backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(1.05);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(1.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  box-shadow: 0 22px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
}

/* If a specific roster area exists, give it extra "arena" glow */
#roster, .section#roster, section#roster{
  background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.50) !important;
  border-color: rgba(211,47,47,0.16);
  box-shadow: 0 28px 120px rgba(0,0,0,0.65), 0 0 0 1px rgba(211,47,47,0.10) inset;
}

/* Keep cards readable while letting decor show */
.player-card{
  background-color: rgba(15,15,15,0.75) !important;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

/* Fix for any elements that set a full black background inline or via strong rules */
[class*="bg-black"], [style*="background:#000"], [style*="background: #000"], [style*="background-color:#000"]{
  background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.58) !important;
}



/* ==============================
   MODE NHL REALISTIC
   (visual ambiance only)
============================== */

/* Ice rink cinematic background */
body {
  background:
    radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 50% -10%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(800px 400px at 20% 30%, rgba(211,47,47,0.28), transparent 65%),
    radial-gradient(800px 400px at 80% 60%, rgba(0,188,212,0.22), transparent 65%),
    linear-gradient(180deg,#020202 0%,#070707 60%,#020202 100%) !important;
}

/* Ice texture overlay */
body::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  pointer-events:none;
  background-image:
    repeating-linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 0px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px,
      transparent 1px,
      transparent 4px
    );
  opacity:0.4;
  mix-blend-mode:overlay;
  z-index:-1;
}

/* Arena moving light beams (NHL style) */
body::after{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:-20%;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    linear-gradient(120deg,
      transparent 0%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 30%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 40%,
      transparent 60%);
  animation: nhlLightSweep 8s linear infinite;
  mix-blend-mode:screen;
  z-index:-1;
}

@keyframes nhlLightSweep{
  0% { transform: translateX(-30%) rotate(2deg); }
  100% { transform: translateX(30%) rotate(2deg); }
}

/* Subtle arena spotlight glow */
.section::before{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  inset:-1px;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(800px 350px at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 70%);
}

/* Slight animated glow for immersive feel */
@keyframes nhlAmbientPulse{
  0%,100% { filter: brightness(1); }
  50% { filter: brightness(1.08); }
}

body {
  animation: nhlAmbientPulse 12s ease-in-out infinite;
}

============================== */
html{

    radial-gradient(1400px 720px at 18% 22%, rgba(211,47,47,0.40), transparent 58%),

}

body{

}

  content:"";

  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;

    repeating-linear-gradient(
      35deg,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.045) 0px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.045) 1px,
      transparent 1px,
      transparent 6px
    );
  opacity: .35;
  mix-blend-mode: overlay;
  z-index: 0;
}

html::after{
  content:"";

  inset: -25%;

    linear-gradient(120deg,
      transparent 0%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.14) 28%,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 40%,
      transparent 60%);

  mix-blend-mode: screen;
  z-index: 0;
}

@keyframes nhlSweepHard{

}

/* Make big page blocks slightly glass so the arena shows */

}

.player-card{

}

        window.addEventListener('load', function() {

                document.getElementById('loading').classList.add('hidden');
            }, 1500);
        });

        // Header scroll
        window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
            const header = document.getElementById('header');
            if (window.pageYOffset > 100) {
                header.classList.add('scrolled');
            } else {
                header.classList.remove('scrolled');
            }
        });

        // Filter players
        function filterPlayers(category) {
            const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.player-card');
            const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn');
            
            buttons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
            event.target.classList.add('active');
            
            cards.forEach(card => {
                if (category === 'all' || card.dataset.position === category) {
                    card.style.display = 'block';
                } else {
                    card.style.display = 'none';
                }
            });
        }

        // Show standings
        function showStandings(type) {
            const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn');
            buttons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
            event.target.classList.add('active');
            
            document.getElementById('standings-pacific').style.display = type === 'pacific' ? 'block' : 'none';
            document.getElementById('standings-all').style.display = type === 'all' ? 'block' : 'none';
        }

        // Smooth scroll
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
                if (target) {
                    target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
                }
            });
        });

        console.log('%cü¶à HAGUENAU SHARKS ü¶à', 'font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #D32F2F;');
        console.log('%c‚úÖ Website loaded successfully!', 'font-size: 16px; color: #4CAF50;');
        console.log('%cüìä 21 Players ‚Ä¢ 32 AHL Teams ‚Ä¢ 8 News Articles', 'font-size: 14px; color: #00BCD4;');
    

        // Safe loading hide (avoid blank screen if loading element missing)
        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            const el = document.getElementById('loading');
            if (el) {
                setTimeout(function() { el.classList.add('hidden'); }, 800);
                setTimeout(function() { el.style.display = 'none'; }, 2000);
            }
        });

        // Player modal: show age/height/weight/nation/position on click (cards keep stats)
        (function(){
            const modal = document.getElementById('playerModal');
            const backdrop = document.getElementById('modalBackdrop');
            const closeBtn = document.getElementById('modalClose');

            const $name = document.getElementById('modalName');
            const $posText = document.getElementById('modalPos');
            const $age = document.getElementById('modalAge');
            const $height = document.getElementById('modalHeight');
            const $weight = document.getElementById('modalWeight');
            const $nation = document.getElementById('modalNation');
            const $position = document.getElementById('modalPosition');

            if(!modal || !backdrop || !$name) return;

            function open(){
                modal.classList.add('open');
                backdrop.classList.add('open');
                document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
            }
            function close(){
                modal.classList.remove('open');
                backdrop.classList.remove('open');
                document.body.style.overflow = '';
            }

            closeBtn && closeBtn.addEventListener('click', close);
            backdrop.addEventListener('click', close);
            window.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{ if(e.key==='Escape') close(); });

            document.querySelectorAll('.player-card').forEach(card=>{
                card.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
                    const name = card.querySelector('.player-name')?.textContent?.trim() || 'JOUEUR';
                    const role = card.dataset.role || card.querySelector('.player-position')?.textContent?.trim() || 'POSITION';
                    $name.textContent = name;
                    $posText.textContent = role;

                    $age.textContent = card.dataset.age || '‚Äî';
                    $height.textContent = card.dataset.height || '‚Äî';
                    $weight.textContent = card.dataset.weight || '‚Äî';
                    $nation.textContent = card.dataset.nation || '‚Äî';
                    $position.textContent = role;

                    open();
                });
            });
        })();

        // More animations: subtle parallax + hover tilt
        (function(){
          const hero = document.querySelector('.hero');
          if(hero){
            let ticking=false;
            window.addEventListener('scroll', ()=>{
              if(ticking) return;
              ticking=true;
              requestAnimationFrame(()=>{
                const y = Math.min(220, window.scrollY * 0.18);
                hero.style.backgroundPosition = `center calc(50% + ${y}px)`;
                ticking=false;
              });
            }, {passive:true});
          }
        })();

        (function(){
          const reduce = window.matchMedia && window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches;
          if(reduce) return;
          const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.player-card');
          cards.forEach(card=>{
            let rect=null;
            card.addEventListener('mouseenter', ()=>{ rect = card.getBoundingClientRect(); card.style.transition='transform .12s ease'; });
            card.addEventListener('mousemove', (e)=>{
              if(!rect) rect=card.getBoundingClientRect();
              const x = (e.clientX - rect.left)/rect.width - .5;
              const y = (e.clientY - rect.top)/rect.height - .5;
              const rx = (-y*8).toFixed(2);
              const ry = (x*10).toFixed(2);
              card.style.transform = `translateY(-10px) rotateX(${rx}deg) rotateY(${ry}deg)`;
            });
            card.addEventListener('mouseleave', ()=>{
              card.style.transition='transform .25s ease';
              card.style.transform='';
              rect=null;
            });
          });
        })();

</script>

<script>
/* ============================
   FIX MENU + POPUP (minimal)
   - Does NOT change design
============================ */
(function(){
  // Smooth scroll for existing menu (nav-link)
  document.querySelectorAll('a.nav-link[href^="#"]').forEach(a=>{
    a.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
      const id = (a.getAttribute('href')||'').slice(1);
      const el = document.getElementById(id);
      if(!el) return;
      e.preventDefault();
      el.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth', block:'start'});
      history.pushState(null,'','#'+id);
    });
  });

  // Modal elements (existing ids in your file)
  const modal = document.getElementById('playerModal');
  const backdrop = document.getElementById('modalBackdrop');
  const closeBtn = document.getElementById('modalClose');

  const $name = document.getElementById('modalName');
  const $posText = document.getElementById('modalPos');
  const $age = document.getElementById('modalAge');
  const $height = document.getElementById('modalHeight');
  const $weight = document.getElementById('modalWeight');
  const $nation = document.getElementById('modalNation');
  const $position = document.getElementById('modalPosition');

  if(!modal || !backdrop) return; // nothing to do

  function openModal(){
    backdrop.classList.add('open');
    modal.classList.add('open');
    document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
  }
  function closeModal(){
    backdrop.classList.remove('open');
    modal.classList.remove('open');
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
  }
  if(closeBtn) closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closeModal);
  backdrop.addEventListener('click', closeModal);
  window.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{ if(e.key==='Escape') closeModal(); });

  function txt(el){ return (el && el.textContent ? el.textContent.trim() : ''); }

  // Guarantee popup on player click (your cards are .player-card)
  document.querySelectorAll('.player-card').forEach(card=>{
    const openFor = ()=>{
      const name = txt(card.querySelector('.player-name')) || card.getAttribute('data-name') || 'Joueur';
      // Position label: priority data-role (Attaquant/D√©fenseur/Gardien), else data-position, else visible text
      const pos = txt(card.querySelector('.player-role')) || card.getAttribute('data-role') || txt(card.querySelector('.player-position')) || card.getAttribute('data-position') || 'Position';

      if($name) $name.textContent = name;
      if($posText) $posText.textContent = pos;

      if($age) $age.textContent = card.getAttribute('data-age') || '‚Äî';
      if($height) $height.textContent = card.getAttribute('data-height') || '‚Äî';
      if($weight) $weight.textContent = card.getAttribute('data-weight') || '‚Äî';
      if($nation) $nation.textContent = card.getAttribute('data-nation') || '‚Äî';
      if($position) $position.textContent = pos;

      openModal();
    };

    card.style.cursor = 'pointer';
    card.setAttribute('tabindex','0');
    card.addEventListener('click', openFor);
    card.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{ if(e.key==='Enter' || e.key===' '){ e.preventDefault(); openFor(); }});
  });
})();
</script>

});
